title: Transcribe Ver 8.40 for Windows
description:
Transcribe Version 8.40 - Get those licks! Windows version

Transcribe is the world's leading software for helping musicians to work out music from recordings. This application has loads of useful functions. It is also used by many people for play-along practice, and also for speech transcription.

Package content:
- Transcribe Ver 8.40 Setup, run this to install Transcribe
- Keygen/Patch, run this to patch Transcribe and to get a key
- Info, this text
- Release notes version 8.40
- Transcribe Flyer, a single-sided information sheet
- Transcribe Screenshot

System requirements : Windows 2000/XP/Vista/7/8

Install instructions:
1. Run Transcribe Ver 8.40 Setup
2. Close Transcribe if opened
3. Copy Keygen/Patch to the folder where Transcribe is installed
3. Run Keygen/Patch
4. Click Patch
5. Choose Transcribe
6. After patching, click Generate to get a Key.
7. Copy the Key to the clipboard
8. Launch Transcribe
9. Click Yes, to accept license agreement
10. Click Help/License info... and then register with the Key

If needed: 
1. Run as Administrator
2. Check that files are not Write Protected
